      "id": "196d394bdb4097e8",
      "subject": "Re: Marketing Project Update",
      "from": "john.doe@gmail.com",
      "date": "Tue, 15 Feb 2022 09:45:00 +0000",
      "snippet": "Hi Maria, Great progress on the project! I&#39;ve attached the updated timeline and the revised marketing materials. Let me know if you need further details or assistance. Best, John",
      "body": "Hi Maria,\n\nGreat progress on the project! I've attached the updated timeline and the revised marketing materials. Let me know if you need further details or assistance.\n\nBest,\nJohn\n"
